properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Tarpon Springs to Suwannee River FL out 20 NM
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued February 11 at 2:34PM EST until February 12 at 10:00AM EST by NWS Tampa Bay Ruskin FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Dense fog will reduce visibility to one nautical mile or
less.

* WHERE...Coastal waters from Tarpon Springs to Suwannee River
FL out 20 NM.

* WHEN...From 10 PM this evening to 10 AM EST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility will make navigation difficult.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 10 PM THIS EVENING TO 10 AM EST WEDNESDAY
